explanation:
System prompt: 'You are a research assistant. Search for [topic], evaluate results, read the 3 most relevant pages. Write a report with: title, 3-paragraph summary, 5 key findings (each cited), and source list. Stop after reading 3 pages.'

Tools: web_search({query}) → [{title, url, snippet}], read_url({url}) → string (truncated), write_report({title, summary, findings, sources}) → {success, filename}

Key details: web_search returns snippets so the agent can evaluate relevance BEFORE reading the full page (saves tokens).
